---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/law-prestige/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Practice Areas | Prestige Law"
  description="Commercial litigation, IP defense, white-collar defense, arbitration, and corporate governance advisory."
  active="practices"
  canonicalPath="/templates/law-prestige/practices"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="py-stack-lg bg-surface border-b border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center min-h-[409px]">
<div class="lg:col-span-8 z-10">
<span class="font-label-md text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 block">Strategic Advocacy</span>
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg mb-lp-stack-md leading-tight">Formidable Legal Capabilities.</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">
                        Unwavering representation for complex high-stakes litigation. We defend the interests of C-suite executives and global corporations with surgical precision and absolute discretion.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-4 relative h-full">
<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-64 h-64 border-t border-r border-secondary/20"></div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Atmospheric Shader Background Element -->
<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/3 h-full opacity-5 pointer-events-none">

</div>
</section>
<!-- Services Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-24 bg-background">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
<!-- 01 Commercial Litigation -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 luxury-card-shadow card-hover-lift transition-all duration-500 border-l-4 border-primary group">
<span class="font-label-md text-outline uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8">01</span>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 200;">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-4">Commercial Litigation</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            Resolution of complex contractual disputes, shareholder litigation, and cross-border commercial conflicts with a focus on risk mitigation.
                        </p>
<a class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest gold-underline-hover inline-block" href="/templates/law-prestige/practices/commercial-litigation">Explore Practice</a>
</div>
<!-- 02 Intellectual Property -->
<div class="bg-primary-container p-10 luxury-card-shadow card-hover-lift transition-all duration-500 border-l-4 border-secondary group">
<span class="font-label-md text-on-primary-container uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8">02</span>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 200;">gavel</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-white mb-4">Intellectual Property</h3>
<p class="text-on-primary-container font-body-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            Securing and defending proprietary assets, from patent infringement to trademark protection in the global digital economy.
                        </p>
<a class="font-label-md text-secondary-fixed uppercase tracking-widest gold-underline-hover inline-block" href="/templates/law-prestige/contact">Explore Practice</a>
</div>
<!-- 03 White Collar Defense -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 luxury-card-shadow card-hover-lift transition-all duration-500 border-l-4 border-primary group">
<span class="font-label-md text-outline uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8">03</span>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 200;">policy</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-4">White Collar Defense</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            Vigorous defense against regulatory investigations, financial crimes, and corporate compliance inquiries at the highest level.
                        </p>
<a class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest gold-underline-hover inline-block" href="/templates/law-prestige/contact">Explore Practice</a>
</div>
<!-- 04 Arbitration & Mediation -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 luxury-card-shadow card-hover-lift transition-all duration-500 border-l-4 border-primary group md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
<span class="font-label-md text-outline uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8">04</span>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 200;">balance</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-4">Arbitration &amp; Mediation</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                            Navigating alternative dispute resolution frameworks to achieve rapid, binding outcomes outside of public courtroom environments.
                        </p>
<a class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest gold-underline-hover inline-block" href="/templates/law-prestige/contact">Explore Practice</a>
</div>
<!-- 05 Corporate Governance -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 luxury-card-shadow card-hover-lift transition-all duration-500 border-l-4 border-primary group lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-gutter">
<div class="flex-1">
<span class="font-label-md text-outline uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8">05</span>
<div class="mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 200;">verified_user</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-4">Corporate Governance</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                                Advising boards and executives on fiduciary duties, disclosure requirements, and institutional integrity standards.
                            </p>
<a class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest gold-underline-hover inline-block" href="/templates/law-prestige/contact">Explore Practice</a>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:block w-1/3 h-full overflow-hidden bg-surface-container">
<img class="object-cover h-full w-full grayscale contrast-125 opacity-70" data-alt="A minimalist architectural shot of a high-end corporate boardroom with dark wood textures and floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking a modern skyline. The lighting is low and sophisticated, reflecting a quiet wealth aesthetic with deep charcoal and champagne gold accents. Sharp focus on geometric lines and textures." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDvO7PQB-0hVkOzZGToZdnMBR8DNLqHrAgXhac8NmhO3cThuNWE1RhsVt1wrP7u8EUUcX1Ncy5anv9iBuxCgBJ2ooRHexVmhPVpPN0Fz9ilSGHum-8XfXRwqA3kqrlsOKyxvcXLfFOzaBR2usAPRhRfqpfO3Ce02YbOuv_hKB7K9IDMai1VFUiSPaUvoHLqmpxhXa8IYsGVLJzz2-je4CAug3GF-hUraow-SJZAZG6efUy_lbYYhVlsNn9sQSvhuIWXxgoxVFwzBfMp"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Mandate Selection Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low border-y border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<span class="font-label-md text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] block mb-4">Engagement Models</span>
<h2 class="font-lp-headline-md text-lp-headline-md mb-4">Mandate Selection</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mx-auto">Tailoring our legal support to the specific phase and intensity of your requirements.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-stretch">
<!-- Advisory Support -->
<div class="bg-white p-12 luxury-card-shadow relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-surface-container opacity-20" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 100;">lightbulb</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-outline-variant/20">Pre-Litigation Advisory</h4>
<ul class="space-y-6 mb-12">
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">check_circle</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase block mb-1">Risk Assessment</span>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Identifying potential liabilities before they escalate into formal disputes.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">check_circle</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase block mb-1">Strategic Planning</span>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Structuring transactions and agreements to minimize litigation exposure.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">check_circle</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase block mb-1">Crisis Management</span>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Immediate counsel for emerging regulatory or public-facing legal issues.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
<button class="w-full py-4 border border-primary font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all duration-300">
                            Select Advisory Mandate
                        </button>
</div>
<!-- Active Litigation -->
<div class="bg-primary-container p-12 luxury-card-shadow relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-secondary-container opacity-10" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 100;">shield</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-white mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-on-tertiary-container/30">Active Litigation Support</h4>
<ul class="space-y-6 mb-12">
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">verified</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase text-secondary-fixed block mb-1">Courtroom Representation</span>
<p class="text-on-primary-container text-sm">Full-scale trial advocacy in federal, state, and international courts.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">verified</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase text-secondary-fixed block mb-1">Discovery &amp; Evidence</span>
<p class="text-on-primary-container text-sm">Aggressive pursuit and preservation of case-critical evidence and intelligence.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed pt-1" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">verified</span>
<div>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase text-secondary-fixed block mb-1">Post-Trial &amp; Appeals</span>
<p class="text-on-primary-container text-sm">Securing favorable judgments and challenging adverse rulings in appellate courts.</p>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
<button class="w-full py-4 bg-secondary text-on-secondary font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-secondary-container hover:text-on-secondary-container transition-all duration-300">
                            Select Litigation Mandate
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-32 bg-background relative">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop text-center">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg mb-8">Secure Your Legacy.</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12 leading-relaxed">
                        In high-value disputes, the difference between success and catastrophic failure is the caliber of your counsel. Partner with Prestige Litigation for uncompromising defense.
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
<button class="px-12 py-5 bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-secondary transition-all duration-300">
                            Book Private Session
                        </button>
<button class="px-12 py-5 border border-primary text-primary font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all duration-300">
                            Download Capabilities
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
